                <p>
                    <h2>More Details</h2>
                <p>Service will be activated only for two weeks: at the end of this period, service would be automatically deactivated</p>
                <p>Only SMS facility will be available once the service is activated; voice calls facility has to be activated separately as per the terms & conditions of IR</p>
                <p>Regular IR SMS rates will be applicable. Please refer to the international SMS rates in the IR tariff guide. Any updates to IR Tariffs will be applicable to SMS Roaming as well</p>
